<br>
But it seems kinda like it would be interesting if people did get VERY wary around mobs. In other words maybe the mobs werent to the point where they had to be swarmed and had massive AOE's where there was no way to avoid people dieing.<br>
<br>
I dunno seems like if you put real scare in people where they said NO WAY am I gonna fight that thing...that it would make legends outta certain players and myths outta certain mobs...<br>
<br>
obviously the leveling couldnt be as cumbersome as EQ...but it would be interesting if it put the fear of god in people... much like real life...we have all done stuff that might put us in harms way but we also guage things so we have the best chance of not dieing, cuz we only go one shot, and avoid it.<br>
<br>
<br>
but yeah it wold probably not make for good gaming...or a lot of timid tradeskillers. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.bellsouth.net/coDataImages/p/Groups/88/88432/pages/410383/ggGRAF2.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
