   Buy a house ( say a straw one ) then build it up over time to a Keep or similar. Defending it would be based on &quot;hiring&quot; NPC Mobs to defend it or certian mobs to Attack. <br>
   Yeah your all thinking people with the most pp will win that 1 ..so you make a Maintenance cost--the larger the house the more pp you have to daily invest..or your house will fall into decay..your guards will leave..ect. Make Class type houses as well ( wizard towers..druids have huge trees..) <br>
   Make them Old zones only, a &quot;key&quot; that gates you home, and have the ability to assign NPC's tasks (patrol..defend...gather food..)<br>
