Back on topic though. I think guild houses would be an interesting idea. Maybe have some different looks you could choose from(casstle, spire, cave system, manor, etc.) where you could have a shared guild bank, arena, forges, looms, kilns, pottery wheels, brew barrels, ovens, PoK book portals and as your guild gets flagged for PoP stones directly to flagged zones, same with raids in LDoN as you succeed in them you get direct ports to wayfarer camps from guild hall.<br>
